➜不要升级Ubuntu的X
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=647	11280
<a href="http://zhcn.blogspot.com/">afa</a> 写道 "<a href="http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=240957">Ubuntu论坛</a>称，升级最新的xserver-xorg-core(版本为1:1.0.2-0ubuntu10.3)会造成X崩溃。这一现象并非仅仅影响Xgl+compiz的用户。
若你不幸升级了，需要：
<blockquote>
<div>wget -c <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~rodarvus/packages/dapper/xorg-server/xserver-xorg-core_1.0.2-0ubuntu10.4_i386.deb">http://people.ubuntu.com/~rodarvus/packages/dapper /xorg-server/xserver-xorg-core_1.0.2-0ubuntu10.4_i 386.deb</a> <br>
wget -c <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~rodarvus/packages/dapper/xorg-server/xserver-xorg-dev_1.0.2-0ubuntu10.4_i386.deb">http://people.ubuntu.com/~rodarvus/packages/dapper /xorg-server/xserver-xorg-dev_1.0.2-0ubuntu10.4_i3 86.deb</a> <br>
sudo dpkg -i xserver-xorg-core*.deb</div> </blockquote>
或者先行降级：
<blockquote>
<div>sudo apt-get install xserver-xorg-core=1:1.0.2-0ubuntu10</div>
</blockquote>
安装了商用显卡驱动（ATI/nVidia）的系统还要重装驱动。"
